In empowering and enlightening our society, Mile Zero Project 2.0 presents you the long awaited competitions.

𝗜𝗗𝗘𝗔𝗖𝗢𝗗𝗘
𝗪𝗘𝗕-𝗫

Don't miss out YOUR CHANCE to be part of THE CHANGE✨

For further inquiries regarding our soon-to-be announced competitions, kindly message us through our DM 📥

#MileZeroProject #MileZeroProject2022 #CaseCompetition #FutureInnovators #NationalCompetition

[[𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐒𝐨𝐨𝐧: 𝐌𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐙𝐞𝐫𝐨 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐣𝐞𝐜𝐭 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟐?]]

Tick… tock… tick… tock…

The clock is ticking because the Mile Zero competition(s) are just coming in a few days! 

Proudly presented to you in the middle of pandemic, the thrill will just as terrific as the competition held offline. Just wait a little bit more for the details👀

For further inquiries, don’t hesitate to hit us up on @milezero.project ’s 📥 DM.

#MileZeroProject #AcceleratingSDGs #MyAppSolutions

Welcoming speech from Coordinating Ministry for Economic Affairs, Rupublic of Indonesia! 🌎

Bapak Rizal Edwin Manansang as the Assistant Deputy Minister for Digital Economy has prepared a special message for you, Fellow Innovators!

As one of our partner, Coordinating Ministry for Economic Affairs can’t wait to share this exciting journey together! 🚀

#MileZeroProject #Kemenko #AcceleratingSDGs #MySmartAppSolution

[[𝐆𝐞𝐭 𝐓𝐨 𝐊𝐧𝐨𝐰: 𝐙𝐞𝐫𝐨𝐂𝐨𝐩!]]

Let’s meet ZeroCop, the unrivaled mascot who inhales the spirit of Mile Zero Project to life. 

Despite the fact that the event may not have begun at this point (it will soon! 👀), ZeroCop will be the one to assist you going through the Mile Zero adventure. ZeroCop will take you to places–to the Digipathways, the competitions, and the more events which will be revealed any sooner.

For further inquiries, don’t hesitate to hit us up on @milezero.project ’s 📥 DM.

Greetings, Future Innovators!

That’s it! It’s a wrap! Mile Zero Project has come to an end, don’t forget to check our recap video!👀

We would like to thank you for your participation and support throughout this event. We hope that you obtained many valuable lessons and experiences to prepare yourself to become the next innovators!

Stay motivated and see you soon 👋

Welcoming Speech by Kabinet Arunika KM ITB. Greetings, Future Innovators!

We have a very special welcoming speech from the President of Kabinet KM ITB!

Please welcome Nada Zharfania Zuhaira!

#MileZeroProject #KMITB

Welcoming Speech by Mile Zero Project. Greetings, Future Innovators!

We have a very special welcoming speech from the project leader of Mile Zero Project!

Please welcome Martinus William Hartono!

#MileZeroProject
